CHANGELOG
=========

* 2.0.0 (2023-XX-XX)

 * move to go.mod
 * remove the `--quiet` option (append `2>/dev/null` to the command instead)
 * remove the `--legacy` option (same as `--git '<1.8.2'`)

 * move information console display to stderr instead of stdout

* 1.0.1 (2017-02-24)

 * add the `--version` flag

* 1.0.0 (2017-01-02)

 * initial version
